lementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9605b39 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9605b39\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-253595e\" data-id=\"253595e\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0dba555 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0dba555\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><p style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 16px\">1) To make heaven.<\/p><p style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 16px\">2) To take as many people with us.<\/p><p style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 16px\">3) To have a member of RCCG in every family of all nations.<\/p><p style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 16px\">4) To accomplish No. 1 above, holiness will be our lifestyle.<\/p><p style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 16px\">5) To accomplish No. 2 and 3 above, we will plant churches within five minutes walking distance in every city and town of developing countries and within five minutes driving distance in every city and town of developed countries.<\/p><p style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 16px\">6) We will pursue these objectives until every Nation in the world is reached for the Lord Jesus Christ<\/p><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-81bdd86\" data-id=\"81bdd86\" data-element_type=\"column